        content: "type: search_result\ntitle: EU Right to Repair law will make it easier to fix a smartphone | Cybernews\nurl: \"https://cybernews.com/tech/right-to-repair/\"\ndescription: \"The directive must be implemented across all EU countries by July 31st, 2026. However, experts say there are loopholes in the law that may prevent users from repairing their devices more easily and at a lower cost.\"\npage_age: \"April 9, 2026\"\nprofile_name: Cybernews\nmeta_url_favicon: \"https://imgs.search.brave.com/YHmcknwxzOBBxYW0aJBCLl0tFWtmZs3Flqo35NbX1nY/rs:fit:32:32:1:0/g:ce/aHR0cDovL2Zhdmlj/b25zLnNlYXJjaC5i/cmF2ZS5jb20vaWNv/bnMvMDIyOTgxNDQ5/NmFkODVlMjU2YzRk/MDNjZjViOWM5Yzgy/OGNmYTM3OTExNzEz/YjZhMDQ5N2ExYTFi/NTBhNDA1NC9jeWJl/cm5ld3MuY29tLw\"\nthumbnail_src: \"https://imgs.search.brave.com/eFxnM_vj_ru1v5MOZ_8k_iZCGePxJsbzaG1cGstXjWk/rs:fit:200:200:1:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9tZWRp/YS5jeWJlcm5ld3Mu/Y29tL2ltYWdlcy9m/ZWF0dXJlZC1iaWcv/MjAyNi8wNC9ldS1y/aWdodC10by1yZXBh/aXIuanBn\"\nthumbnail_original: \"https://media.cybernews.com/images/featured-big/2026/04/eu-right-to-repair.jpg\"\nextra_snippets: \"The European Union’s Right to Repair directive aims to make smartphone, tablet, and household appliance repairs easier and more affordable. However, experts say that manufacturers may still be holding the cards. ... The EU Right to Repair directive will be implemented across all EU countries by July 31st, 2026.|The directive must be implemented across all EU countries by July 31st, 2026. However, experts say there are loopholes in the law that may prevent users from repairing their devices more easily and at a lower cost.|Americans are also fighting for cheaper and easier repairs. According to the Public Interest Research Group, a consumer protection advocacy group, about one-third of Americans live in a state that has passed some form of Right to Repair policy as of February 2026.|ShinyHunters impersonator claims to have hacked Nvidia’s GeForce Now. Here's what Nvidia told us 05 May 2026\"\nhash: 6d4a777fe4b3401a\nembed_ref: cybernews.com-Ppc\napp_id: web\nskill_id: search",
